2023-12-26 15:31:10.441 +07:00 [INF] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command
Executed DbCommand (84ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Username], [t2].[Password], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t].[OrderStatusId], [t].[Name], [t].[FullName], [t].[CreatedTime], [t0].[ProductName], [t0].[RegisterOpenTime], [t0].[RegisterClosedTime], [t0].[OpenTime], [t0].[ClosedTime], [t0].[c]
FROM (
    SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [o].[AuctionProductId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE ((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[RegisterOpenTime], [t1].[RegisterClosedTime], [t1].[OpenTime], [t1].[ClosedTime], [t1].[c], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [a1].[RegisterOpenTime], [a1].[RegisterClosedTime], [a1].[OpenTime], [a1].[ClosedTime], 1 AS [c], [a1].[Id], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [a1].[Id] ORDER BY [a1].[Id], [p].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a1]
        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a1].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
        WHERE [p].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AuctionProductId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o2].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id]

Executed DbCommand (109ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Username], [t2].[Password], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t].[OrderStatusId], [t].[Name], [t].[FullName], [t].[CreatedTime], [t0].[ProductName], [t0].[RegisterOpenTime], [t0].[RegisterClosedTime], [t0].[OpenTime], [t0].[ClosedTime], [t0].[c]
FROM (
    SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [o].[AuctionProductId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE ((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[RegisterOpenTime], [t1].[RegisterClosedTime], [t1].[OpenTime], [t1].[ClosedTime], [t1].[c], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [a1].[RegisterOpenTime], [a1].[RegisterClosedTime], [a1].[OpenTime], [a1].[ClosedTime], 1 AS [c], [a1].[Id], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [a1].[Id] ORDER BY [a1].[Id], [p].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a1]
        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a1].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
        WHERE [p].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AuctionProductId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o2].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id]

    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY

) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[OrderId]

2023-12-26 15:44:23.434 +07:00 [INF] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command
Executed DbCommand (87ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Username], [t2].[Password], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t].[OrderStatusId], [t].[Name], [t].[FullName], [t].[CreatedTime], [t0].[ProductName], [t0].[RegisterOpenTime], [t0].[RegisterClosedTime], [t0].[OpenTime], [t0].[ClosedTime], [t0].[c]
FROM (
    SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [o].[AuctionProductId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE ((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[RegisterOpenTime], [t1].[RegisterClosedTime], [t1].[OpenTime], [t1].[ClosedTime], [t1].[c], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [a1].[RegisterOpenTime], [a1].[RegisterClosedTime], [a1].[OpenTime], [a1].[ClosedTime], 1 AS [c], [a1].[Id], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [a1].[Id] ORDER BY [a1].[Id], [p].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a1]
        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a1].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
        WHERE [p].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1

    SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [o].[AuctionProductId]

    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE ((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (

    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AuctionProductId] = [t0].[Id]

) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[OrderId]

2023-12-26 15:46:49.651 +07:00 [INF] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command
Executed DbCommand (81ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Username], [t2].[Password], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t].[OrderStatusId], [t].[Name], [t].[FullName], [t].[CreatedTime], [t0].[ProductName], [t0].[RegisterOpenTime], [t0].[RegisterClosedTime], [t0].[OpenTime], [t0].[ClosedTime], [t0].[c]
FROM (
    SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [o].[AuctionProductId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE ((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[RegisterOpenTime], [t1].[RegisterClosedTime], [t1].[OpenTime], [t1].[ClosedTime], [t1].[c], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [a1].[RegisterOpenTime], [a1].[RegisterClosedTime], [a1].[OpenTime], [a1].[ClosedTime], 1 AS [c], [a1].[Id], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [a1].[Id] ORDER BY [a1].[Id], [p].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a1]
        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a1].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
        WHERE [p].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AuctionProductId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o2].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [o].[Id], [o].[OrderTypeId], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o0].[Name], [o1].[Name] AS [Name0], [a0].[FullName], [o].[Note], [o].[Note2], [o].[Note3], [o].[Note4], [o].[Note5], [o].[CreatedTime], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [o].[AuctionProductId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE (((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o].[Id] = @__orderId_0)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[RegisterOpenTime], [t1].[RegisterClosedTime], [t1].[OpenTime], [t1].[ClosedTime], [t1].[c], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [a1].[RegisterOpenTime], [a1].[RegisterClosedTime], [a1].[OpenTime], [a1].[ClosedTime], 1 AS [c], [a1].[Id], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [a1].[Id] ORDER BY [a1].[Id], [p].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a1]
        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a1].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
        WHERE [p].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AuctionProductId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o2].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [o].[AuctionProductId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE ((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[RegisterOpenTime], [t1].[RegisterClosedTime], [t1].[OpenTime], [t1].[ClosedTime], [t1].[c], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [a1].[RegisterOpenTime], [a1].[RegisterClosedTime], [a1].[OpenTime], [a1].[ClosedTime], 1 AS [c], [a1].[Id], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [a1].[Id] ORDER BY [a1].[Id], [p].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a1]
        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a1].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
        WHERE [p].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AuctionProductId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o2].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id]

    SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [o].[AuctionProductId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]

    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]

    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[RegisterOpenTime], [t1].[RegisterClosedTime], [t1].[OpenTime], [t1].[ClosedTime], [t1].[c], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [a1].[RegisterOpenTime], [a1].[RegisterClosedTime], [a1].[OpenTime], [a1].[ClosedTime], 1 AS [c], [a1].[Id], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [a1].[Id] ORDER BY [a1].[Id], [p].[Id]) AS [row]

        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a1].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
        WHERE [p].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AuctionProductId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (

    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]

) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[OrderId]

Executed DbCommand (73ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Username], [t2].[Password], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t].[OrderStatusId], [t].[Name], [t].[FullName], [t].[CreatedTime], [t0].[ProductName], [t0].[RegisterOpenTime], [t0].[RegisterClosedTime], [t0].[OpenTime], [t0].[ClosedTime], [t0].[c]
FROM (
    SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [o].[AuctionProductId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE ((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[RegisterOpenTime], [t1].[RegisterClosedTime], [t1].[OpenTime], [t1].[ClosedTime], [t1].[c], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [a1].[RegisterOpenTime], [a1].[RegisterClosedTime], [a1].[OpenTime], [a1].[ClosedTime], 1 AS [c], [a1].[Id], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [a1].[Id] ORDER BY [a1].[Id], [p].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a1]
        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a1].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
        WHERE [p].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AuctionProductId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o2].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Username], [t2].[Password], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t].[OrderStatusId], [t].[Name], [t].[FullName], [t].[CreatedTime], [t0].[ProductName], [t0].[RegisterOpenTime], [t0].[RegisterClosedTime], [t0].[OpenTime], [t0].[ClosedTime], [t0].[c]
FROM (
    SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [o].[AuctionProductId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE ((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[RegisterOpenTime], [t1].[RegisterClosedTime], [t1].[OpenTime], [t1].[ClosedTime], [t1].[c], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [a1].[RegisterOpenTime], [a1].[RegisterClosedTime], [a1].[OpenTime], [a1].[ClosedTime], 1 AS [c], [a1].[Id], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [a1].[Id] ORDER BY [a1].[Id], [p].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a1]
        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a1].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
        WHERE [p].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AuctionProductId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o2].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id]

    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[RegisterOpenTime], [t1].[RegisterClosedTime], [t1].[OpenTime], [t1].[ClosedTime], [t1].[c], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [a1].[RegisterOpenTime], [a1].[RegisterClosedTime], [a1].[OpenTime], [a1].[ClosedTime], 1 AS [c], [a1].[Id], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [a1].[Id] ORDER BY [a1].[Id], [p].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a1]
        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a1].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
        WHERE [p].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AuctionProductId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o2].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id]

Executed DbCommand (80ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Username], [t2].[Password], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t].[OrderStatusId], [t].[Name], [t].[FullName], [t].[CreatedTime], [t0].[ProductName], [t0].[RegisterOpenTime], [t0].[RegisterClosedTime], [t0].[OpenTime], [t0].[ClosedTime], [t0].[c]
FROM (
    SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [o].[AuctionProductId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE ((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[RegisterOpenTime], [t1].[RegisterClosedTime], [t1].[OpenTime], [t1].[ClosedTime], [t1].[c], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [a1].[RegisterOpenTime], [a1].[RegisterClosedTime], [a1].[OpenTime], [a1].[ClosedTime], 1 AS [c], [a1].[Id], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [a1].[Id] ORDER BY [a1].[Id], [p].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a1]
        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a1].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
        WHERE [p].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AuctionProductId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o2].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [o].[AuctionProductId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE ((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[RegisterOpenTime], [t1].[RegisterClosedTime], [t1].[OpenTime], [t1].[ClosedTime], [t1].[c], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [a1].[RegisterOpenTime], [a1].[RegisterClosedTime], [a1].[OpenTime], [a1].[ClosedTime], 1 AS [c], [a1].[Id], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [a1].[Id] ORDER BY [a1].[Id], [p].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a1]
        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a1].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
        WHERE [p].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AuctionProductId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o2].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[RegisterOpenTime], [t1].[RegisterClosedTime], [t1].[OpenTime], [t1].[ClosedTime], [t1].[c], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [a1].[RegisterOpenTime], [a1].[RegisterClosedTime], [a1].[OpenTime], [a1].[ClosedTime], 1 AS [c], [a1].[Id], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [a1].[Id] ORDER BY [a1].[Id], [p].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a1]
        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a1].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
        WHERE [p].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AuctionProductId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o2].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [o].[AuctionProductId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE ((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[RegisterOpenTime], [t1].[RegisterClosedTime], [t1].[OpenTime], [t1].[ClosedTime], [t1].[c], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]

        SELECT [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [a1].[RegisterOpenTime], [a1].[RegisterClosedTime], [a1].[OpenTime], [a1].[ClosedTime], 1 AS [c], [a1].[Id], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [a1].[Id] ORDER BY [a1].[Id], [p].[Id]) AS [row]

        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a1].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
        WHERE [p].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AuctionProductId] = [t0].[Id]

    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Username], [t2].[Password], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t].[OrderStatusId], [t].[Name], [t].[FullName], [t].[CreatedTime], [t0].[ProductName], [t0].[RegisterOpenTime], [t0].[RegisterClosedTime], [t0].[OpenTime], [t0].[ClosedTime], [t0].[c]
FROM (
    SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [o].[AuctionProductId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE ((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[RegisterOpenTime], [t1].[RegisterClosedTime], [t1].[OpenTime], [t1].[ClosedTime], [t1].[c], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [a1].[RegisterOpenTime], [a1].[RegisterClosedTime], [a1].[OpenTime], [a1].[ClosedTime], 1 AS [c], [a1].[Id], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [a1].[Id] ORDER BY [a1].[Id], [p].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a1]
        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a1].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
        WHERE [p].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AuctionProductId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o2].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id]

    FROM (
        SELECT [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [a1].[RegisterOpenTime], [a1].[RegisterClosedTime], [a1].[OpenTime], [a1].[ClosedTime], 1 AS [c], [a1].[Id], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [a1].[Id] ORDER BY [a1].[Id], [p].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a1]
        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a1].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
        WHERE [p].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AuctionProductId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o2].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [o].[AuctionProductId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE ((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[RegisterOpenTime], [t1].[RegisterClosedTime], [t1].[OpenTime], [t1].[ClosedTime], [t1].[c], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [a1].[RegisterOpenTime], [a1].[RegisterClosedTime], [a1].[OpenTime], [a1].[ClosedTime], 1 AS [c], [a1].[Id], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [a1].[Id] ORDER BY [a1].[Id], [p].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a1]
        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a1].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
        WHERE [p].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AuctionProductId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o2].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Username], [t2].[Password], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t].[OrderStatusId], [t].[Name], [t].[FullName], [t].[CreatedTime], [t0].[ProductName], [t0].[RegisterOpenTime], [t0].[RegisterClosedTime], [t0].[OpenTime], [t0].[ClosedTime], [t0].[c]
FROM (
    SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [o].[AuctionProductId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE ((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[RegisterOpenTime], [t1].[RegisterClosedTime], [t1].[OpenTime], [t1].[ClosedTime], [t1].[c], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [a1].[RegisterOpenTime], [a1].[RegisterClosedTime], [a1].[OpenTime], [a1].[ClosedTime], 1 AS [c], [a1].[Id], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [a1].[Id] ORDER BY [a1].[Id], [p].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a1]
        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a1].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
        WHERE [p].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AuctionProductId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o2].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id]

Executed DbCommand (83ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Username], [t2].[Password], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t].[OrderStatusId], [t].[Name], [t].[FullName], [t].[CreatedTime], [t0].[ProductName], [t0].[RegisterOpenTime], [t0].[RegisterClosedTime], [t0].[OpenTime], [t0].[ClosedTime], [t0].[c]
FROM (
    SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [o].[AuctionProductId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE ((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[RegisterOpenTime], [t1].[RegisterClosedTime], [t1].[OpenTime], [t1].[ClosedTime], [t1].[c], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [a1].[RegisterOpenTime], [a1].[RegisterClosedTime], [a1].[OpenTime], [a1].[ClosedTime], 1 AS [c], [a1].[Id], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [a1].[Id] ORDER BY [a1].[Id], [p].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a1]
        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a1].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
        WHERE [p].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AuctionProductId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o2].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id]

    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]

    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
) AS [t]

        FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a1]
        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a1].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
        WHERE [p].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AuctionProductId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (

    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]

) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[OrderId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[OrderTypeId], [t].[OrderStatusId], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Username], [t2].[Password], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t].[Name], [t].[Name0], [t].[FullName], [t].[Note], [t].[Note2], [t].[Note3], [t].[Note4], [t].[Note5], [t].[CreatedTime], [t0].[ProductName], [t0].[RegisterOpenTime], [t0].[RegisterClosedTime], [t0].[OpenTime], [t0].[ClosedTime], [t0].[c]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [o].[Id], [o].[OrderTypeId], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o0].[Name], [o1].[Name] AS [Name0], [a0].[FullName], [o].[Note], [o].[Note2], [o].[Note3], [o].[Note4], [o].[Note5], [o].[CreatedTime], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [o].[AuctionProductId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE (((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o].[Id] = @__orderId_0)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[RegisterOpenTime], [t1].[RegisterClosedTime], [t1].[OpenTime], [t1].[ClosedTime], [t1].[c], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [a1].[RegisterOpenTime], [a1].[RegisterClosedTime], [a1].[OpenTime], [a1].[ClosedTime], 1 AS [c], [a1].[Id], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [a1].[Id] ORDER BY [a1].[Id], [p].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a1]
        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a1].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
        WHERE [p].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AuctionProductId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o2].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [o].[AuctionProductId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE ((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[RegisterOpenTime], [t1].[RegisterClosedTime], [t1].[OpenTime], [t1].[ClosedTime], [t1].[c], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [a1].[RegisterOpenTime], [a1].[RegisterClosedTime], [a1].[OpenTime], [a1].[ClosedTime], 1 AS [c], [a1].[Id], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [a1].[Id] ORDER BY [a1].[Id], [p].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a1]
        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a1].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
        WHERE [p].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AuctionProductId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o2].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Username], [t2].[Password], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t].[OrderStatusId], [t].[Name], [t].[FullName], [t].[CreatedTime], [t0].[ProductName], [t0].[RegisterOpenTime], [t0].[RegisterClosedTime], [t0].[OpenTime], [t0].[ClosedTime], [t0].[c]
FROM (
    SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [o].[AuctionProductId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE ((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[RegisterOpenTime], [t1].[RegisterClosedTime], [t1].[OpenTime], [t1].[ClosedTime], [t1].[c], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [a1].[RegisterOpenTime], [a1].[RegisterClosedTime], [a1].[OpenTime], [a1].[ClosedTime], 1 AS [c], [a1].[Id], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [a1].[Id] ORDER BY [a1].[Id], [p].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a1]
        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a1].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
        WHERE [p].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AuctionProductId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o2].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id]

        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a1].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]

    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AuctionProductId] = [t0].[Id]

) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[OrderId]

) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[OrderId]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [o].[Id], [o].[OrderTypeId], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o0].[Name], [o1].[Name] AS [Name0], [a0].[FullName], [o].[Note], [o].[Note2], [o].[Note3], [o].[Note4], [o].[Note5], [o].[CreatedTime], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [o].[AuctionProductId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE (((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o].[Id] = @__orderId_0)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[RegisterOpenTime], [t1].[RegisterClosedTime], [t1].[OpenTime], [t1].[ClosedTime], [t1].[c], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [a1].[RegisterOpenTime], [a1].[RegisterClosedTime], [a1].[OpenTime], [a1].[ClosedTime], 1 AS [c], [a1].[Id], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [a1].[Id] ORDER BY [a1].[Id], [p].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a1]
        INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a1].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
        WHERE [p].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AuctionProductId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o2].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id]

WHERE (((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([o].[OrderId] = @__obj_Id_0)) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)
ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
